title: NES Emulator w/ ROMs [Cobra ODE] PS3
description:
NES Emulator with ROMs

PS3 Cobra ODE ISO

Load ISO
select dev_bdvd
Select ROM

To add ROMs just Extract ISO and place ROMs with current ROMs in folder
then convert back to ISO with Cobras GenPS3ISO Program.

Included ROMs
Batman, Castlevania, Contra, Excite-Bike, Mario 1,2 and 3, Metroid,
Prince of Persia, Punch-Out, Rampage, Rampart, Renegade, Simpsons - B.vs.SM
Spelunker, Yo Noid, Zelda
